# ============================================================================
# Anthropic API key — REQUIRED.
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your real key.
# Never commit .env or .env.local — see .gitignore.
# ============================================================================
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# ============================================================================
# Model used by /api/chat. Restart `npm run dev` after changing.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Available models (price per 1M tokens — input / output):
#
#   claude-opus-4-7    Most capable. Adaptive thinking + effort up to "max".  $15 / $75
#   claude-opus-4-6    Same Opus tier, slightly cheaper.                       $5 / $25
#   claude-sonnet-4-6  Best balance of intelligence vs cost.                   $3 / $15
#   claude-haiku-4-5   Fastest & cheapest. Does NOT support thinking/effort.  $1 / $5
#
# Notes:
# - Haiku 4.5 will return 400 if `thinking` or `output_config.effort` is sent,
#   so the handler auto-disables both when model id contains "haiku".
# - Default if unset: claude-opus-4-7
# ============================================================================
ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-opus-4-7

# ============================================================================
# Reasoning effort. Higher = more thinking tokens, better quality, more cost.
# Leave EMPTY to omit (recommended for Haiku 4.5).
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Available values:
#
#   low      Minimal reasoning. Cheapest. Good for short factual answers.
#   medium   Balanced.
#   high     More thorough. Recommended for intelligence-sensitive tasks.
#   xhigh    Opus 4.7 only — best for coding/agentic loops.
#   max      Opus tier only (Opus 4.6+) — maximum reasoning. NOT for Sonnet/Haiku.
#
# Default if unset: omitted (model decides — usually equivalent to "high").
# An invalid value here will fail at startup with a clear error message.
# ============================================================================
ANTHROPIC_EFFORT=medium
